body: Number column only links to reviewable. Branch now links to GitHub. Moved username tooltip to title column. Tooltips prettier and better aligned. Oh, and branches and text in the title should now break after underscores and never in the middle of words. --- This change is [](https://reviewable.io/reviews/toktok/website/32)
